column5: Yep, that would be my ride out of here.  Heading up to fly with Cochrane Air into Mikwam for some trophy northerns and walleye.  Stay tuned for the report!  See you in a few days!
Have a great trip Will & best of luck up there.
Exciting.  Hope the weather and skeeters are kind to ya.  Have a good time.
Have a good one will! I will be awaiting that report!  G
Have a great time  and I am sure I don't have to say it      lots of pictures...please  oh well I said it anyways
Thanks guys and of course there will be lots of pics  .  I'll try to check in later if I can but this will most likely be it till next week.
